{"tid":1864775,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廣東鼓勵舉報湖北人行蹤 報料者獲賞30個口罩","createTime":"2020-02-05T19:25:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T19:28:40.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f5185858fa90766af65b29d5e40d441568ae19","tid":1864775,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T19:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/wZZjInmbWaXsjAhbB9kOXaLjG7s=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/6SKEPWR67PHPMC7K64KU5KXGHM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FwZZjInmbWaXsjAhbB9kOXaLjG7s%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F6SKEPWR67PHPMC7K64KU5KXGHM.jpg&h=7154daaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梅州三角鎮宣佈，向舉報湖北人行蹤的民眾獎賞30個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒疫情越演越烈，各地口罩匱乏，連香港也出現「搶罩潮」。近日廣東梅州三角鎮發出通告，獎勵民眾及時提供線索協助排查從湖北省進入當地的人，每核實1人將獲獎勵30個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n《南方都市報》報道，約有人口5萬的廣東省梅州市梅江區三角鎮近日發佈一份公告，內容指民眾提供線索，協助排查從湖北省進入當地的外來人口、湖北省回到梅州的當地戶籍人士，每核實1人將獎勵30個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述三角鎮政府相關負責人表示，自當地疫情防控指揮部成立以來，該鎮17個村社區已排查到140名從湖北來往的人員。負責人又指，由於全國多地出現過確診患者有意隱瞞來往湖北行程的情況，為了避免同類情況，鎮政府採取有關措施，向鎮上村民徵集湖北來往人員線索，阻斷疫情擴散的可能。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，自公告發出3天以來，當地已徵集到1、2個新的「有用線索」，正在加緊核實相關情況。<br />\n<br />\n中央社/《南方都市報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200205/JBCVIVNLXFV3VP73QKKLEGQCRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200205%2FJBCVIVNLXFV3VP73QKKLEGQCRA%2F&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iStzr7MFgrQ0V0XG6LyL0fmAc%3D&h=b7cc340b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200205%2FJBCVIVNLXFV3VP73QKKLEGQCRA%2F&h=71dc3559\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200205/JBCVIVNLXFV3VP73QKKLEGQCRA/</a>"},{"pid":"ad372c17fe621692e572463a1a05d8272df43b47","tid":1864775,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,